269
00:15:09,810 --> 00:15:11,740
I won't sleep.

270
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:13,570
It's too fun.

271
00:15:23,340 --> 00:15:25,260
Gosh.

272
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:29,590
[Staring]

273
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:35,780
I like this musician.

274
00:15:35,780 --> 00:15:38,530
