283
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:39,600
I couldn't sleep.

284
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,670
I want coffee.

285
00:16:41,670 --> 00:16:43,520
Coffee?

286
00:16:43,520 --> 00:16:46,550
You want to force your brain to wake up?

287
00:16:49,370 --> 00:16:54,690
