289
00:16:59,730 --> 00:17:01,710
[Startled]

290
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:05,820
It's like we're on a ride.

291
00:17:07,470 --> 00:17:09,800
So Yun is always relaxed.

292
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:13,500
