- I do.

293
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:15,920
- It's written on your face.
- They're friends now.

294
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:18,750
[Tokushima]

295
00:17:19,750 --> 00:17:22,640
[A place with simple charm]

296
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:32,020
- I love small cities in Japan.
- They're nice.

297
00:17:35,520 --> 00:17:37,790
[A lot to see and eat]

298
00:17:39,290 --> 00:17:43,020
[What feelings will they develop here?]

299
00:17:43,020 --> 00:17:44,760
They must be so excited.

300
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:46,780
[Tokushima Airport]

301
00:17:46,780 --> 00:17:48,000
