302
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:50,070
That's my dance move.

303
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:52,890
[Tokushima is welcoming them
with sunny weather]

304
00:17:52,890 --> 00:17:54,350
Wow, it's amazing.

305
00:17:54,350 --> 00:17:56,870
Wow, the weather is amazing.

306
00:17:56,870 --> 00:17:58,670
It's so nice.

307
00:17:58,670 --> 00:18:03,640
[Taking a jumbo taxi to the next destination]

308
00:18:04,980 --> 00:18:09,870
