310
00:18:13,350 --> 00:18:16,630
Wow, the buildings are so cute, too.

311
00:18:16,630 --> 00:18:18,750
It really feels like a small town.

312
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:20,140
So nice.

313
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:22,580
This is so Japan.

314
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:24,220
The vending machines. The vending machines.

315
00:18:24,220 --> 00:18:26,180
We need to get a soda.

316
00:18:26,180 --> 00:18:29,080
That's the jelly. It finally feels real.

317
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:32,500
Let's make a ton of fun memories.

318
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:34,250
I'm so jealous.

319
00:18:34,250 --> 00:18:36,380
Gyu Ri and Seo Won?

320
00:18:36,380 --> 00:18:37,640
[Tap, tap]

321
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:39,880
