324
00:18:52,190 --> 00:18:53,550
[So heart-fluttering]

325
00:18:53,550 --> 00:18:55,370
That's right.

326
00:18:55,370 --> 00:18:58,280
Wasn't Seo Won so cute just now?
He tapped her like this.

327
00:18:58,280 --> 00:18:59,700
He's smooth.

328
00:18:59,700 --> 00:19:03,000
[Seo Won was so approachable]

329
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:05,160
- He's smooth.
- I know.

330
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:06,120
He tapped her like this.

331
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:08,520
They looked nice together just now.

332
00:19:08,520 --> 00:19:10,640
Wow, what's that?

333
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:12,360
Wow.

334
00:19:12,360 --> 00:19:14,370
It feels like summer here.

335
00:19:14,370 --> 00:19:16,200
It's so pretty.

336
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:18,700
[Tap]

337
00:19:20,270 --> 00:19:23,750
The Great Naruto Bridge
