343
00:19:41,010 --> 00:19:43,790
This is going to get them excited.

344
00:19:43,790 --> 00:19:45,600
[Boarding the cruise boat
at the Naruto Strait]

345
00:19:48,690 --> 00:19:50,970
- Wow.
- Seriously.

346
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:53,200
For real.

347
00:19:53,230 --> 00:19:54,710
It feels surreal.

348
00:19:54,710 --> 00:19:56,590
This is so Japan.

349
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:59,820
It's a true Japanese boat.

350
00:19:59,820 --> 00:20:04,630
The rocky boat brings you closer together.

351
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:12,950
