352
00:20:12,950 --> 00:20:14,740
This is so crazy!

353
00:20:14,740 --> 00:20:16,910
Wow, this is so nice.

354
00:20:16,910 --> 00:20:20,310
[The ocean makes you feel refreshed]

355
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:25,980
