356
00:20:25,980 --> 00:20:29,690
- I'll be a better person.
- My stress is going away!

357
00:20:29,700 --> 00:20:33,100
Wow, it's so pretty. Seriously.

358
00:20:34,290 --> 00:20:35,260
So handsome.

359
00:20:35,260 --> 00:20:39,240
Why are you smiling so sweetly at me?

360
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:40,770
[Hehe]

361
00:20:40,770 --> 00:20:42,340
You look nice.

362
00:20:42,990 --> 00:20:44,840
[Capturing his sweet smile]

363
00:20:44,900 --> 00:20:47,400
- They're such good-looking people.
- It's like a commercial.

364
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:49,690
- I like it.
- You do?

365
00:20:50,450 --> 00:20:51,970
I like the one with a smile.

366
00:20:51,970 --> 00:20:54,950
Look at that whirlpool.

367
00:20:54,950 --> 00:20:58,420
