369
00:21:04,870 --> 00:21:06,630
I'll be a better person.

370
00:21:06,630 --> 00:21:09,210
That's how the current gets pulled together.

371
00:21:09,210 --> 00:21:10,230
So crazy.

372
00:21:10,230 --> 00:21:11,980
Let me win the lottery.

373
00:21:11,980 --> 00:21:13,840
[Grabbing]

374
00:21:14,460 --> 00:21:16,540
Wow, so crazy.

375
00:21:16,540 --> 00:21:18,480
- Wow.
- It must look cool from above.

376
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:20,540
I thought we were going there.

377
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:27,940
It makes you zone out.

378
00:21:27,940 --> 00:21:29,010
Water hypnosis.

379
00:21:29,010 --> 00:21:33,010
- Wow.
- This is making us want to go on a trip.

380
00:21:33,010 --> 00:21:35,280
So crazy.

381
00:21:36,180 --> 00:21:38,520
[Glancing]

382
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:41,440
It's like our relationship.

383
00:21:42,250 --> 00:21:44,680
It's like our life.

384
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:47,520
This represents our relationships.

385
00:21:47,520 --> 00:21:53,030
[Are their feelings whirlpooling, too?]

386
00:21:54,980 --> 00:21:57,560
This is making me want to scream.

387
00:21:57,560 --> 00:21:58,720
Daebak.

388
00:21:58,720 --> 00:22:01,120
Gyu Ri is on edge.

389
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:03,790
- What are they doing?
- I don't know.

390
00:22:03,790 --> 00:22:05,710
[Screaming at the blue ocean]

391
00:22:06,580 --> 00:22:09,020
I'll be a better person!

392
00:22:12,530 --> 00:22:15,000
I kept my promise.

393
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:19,000
- So cute.
- They look so cool together.

394
00:22:19,010 --> 00:22:20,610
[Staring]

395
00:22:20,610 --> 00:22:24,000
She keeps looking. She's very aware of them.

396
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:27,600
How nice.

397
00:22:28,500 --> 00:22:30,220
I'll stand here.

398
00:22:30,220 --> 00:22:34,330
[Gyu Ri is standing in the sun]

399
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:48,800
- He must be torn.
- I know. Go to her.

400
00:22:48,800 --> 00:22:52,930
