404
00:23:03,450 --> 00:23:05,390
I screamed just now.

405
00:23:06,340 --> 00:23:09,060
I saw you. I'm jealous.

406
00:23:12,950 --> 00:23:14,500
[Glancing]

407
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:17,830
- Can I call you Noona?
- Noona?

408
00:23:17,900 --> 00:23:20,110
- Noona?
- Yes.

409
00:23:20,110 --> 00:23:21,730
Noona?

410
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:26,610
Okay.

411
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:28,780
Really?

412
00:23:28,780 --> 00:23:31,940
I've never been called Noona.

413
00:23:31,940 --> 00:23:33,930
I'm not used to it, either.

414
00:23:33,930 --> 00:23:36,310
Come on. You've only dated older women.

415
00:23:36,310 --> 00:23:38,910
Maybe I didn't call them that.

416
00:23:38,910 --> 00:23:41,440
- What?
- I feel embarrassed.

417
00:23:41,440 --> 00:23:43,020
I feel embarrassed.

418
00:23:43,970 --> 00:23:46,840
- Stare at the water, then.
- I might as well.

419
00:23:46,840 --> 00:23:48,380
Yes.

420
00:23:53,320 --> 00:23:55,320
How did you feel the past week?

421
00:23:55,320 --> 00:23:57,660
The past week?

422
00:23:57,660 --> 00:23:59,390
I need to tell you, right?

423
00:23:59,390 --> 00:24:01,270
- How did I feel?
- That was your answer.

424
00:24:01,270 --> 00:24:02,800
No, no.

425
00:24:03,520 --> 00:24:05,530
How did I feel?

426
00:24:05,530 --> 00:24:08,470
You haven't fully adjusted yet, right?

427
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:13,240
After this trip...

428
00:24:14,910 --> 00:24:16,490
I think...

429
00:24:17,290 --> 00:24:19,230
You'll develop a feeling?

430
00:24:19,230 --> 00:24:20,910
I get that feeling.

431
00:24:20,910 --> 00:24:23,870
This is a real trip.

432
00:24:23,870 --> 00:24:26,280
It will be so memorable.

433
00:24:30,690 --> 00:24:34,900
