434
00:24:34,900 --> 00:24:37,740
I actually want
Seo Won and Gyu Ri to work out.

435
00:24:37,740 --> 00:24:39,430
I know. I do, too.

436
00:24:39,430 --> 00:24:42,280
Seo Won makes her feel secure.

437
00:24:42,280 --> 00:24:45,970
Wu Yeol makes her a bit nervous.

438
00:24:45,970 --> 00:24:49,300
Gyu Ri needs to feel secure. Seriously.

439
00:24:49,300 --> 00:24:54,930
[Heading to lunch after the boat ride]

440
00:24:55,620 --> 00:24:58,740
There's a vending machine
in the middle of the road.

441
00:24:58,740 --> 00:25:00,650
It's so romantic.

442
00:25:01,630 --> 00:25:02,660
Take pictures.

443
00:25:02,660 --> 00:25:05,210
