467
00:26:02,910 --> 00:26:06,910
- Eight orders, please.
- Eight orders. Thank you.

468
00:26:06,910 --> 00:26:08,510
Thank you.

469
00:26:08,510 --> 00:26:11,670
[Applauding at the successful order]

470
00:26:11,670 --> 00:26:12,760
He's cute.

471
00:26:12,760 --> 00:26:17,930
[The ramen is being prepared immediately]

472
00:26:27,710 --> 00:26:31,500
