521
00:29:04,570 --> 00:29:07,280
- No.
- I don't care about that.

522
00:29:07,280 --> 00:29:09,740
- Really?
- Wow, I like it.

523
00:29:09,740 --> 00:29:13,680
[Individual dates instead of a group date]

524
00:29:14,050 --> 00:29:15,620
[Suppressing]

525
00:29:17,330 --> 00:29:19,500
What should we do?

526
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:23,700
- What do we do?
- Yu Gyeong is looking at him again.

527
00:29:23,700 --> 00:29:26,500
- Huh?
- Everyone turned into sea breams.

528
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:30,660
[Who will they spend time with?]

529
00:29:30,660 --> 00:29:33,090
But we have tomorrow, too.

530
00:29:33,090 --> 00:29:34,830
- Right.
- Tomorrow is another day.

531
00:29:34,830 --> 00:29:36,990
Tomorrow is another day?

532
00:29:41,590 --> 00:29:43,790
I can't eat anymore.

533
00:29:47,370 --> 00:29:49,050
