She did speak to Seo Won at length.

2072
01:52:09,980 --> 01:52:11,950
[I don't think so]

2073
01:52:11,950 --> 01:52:13,670
But to be honest,

2074
01:52:13,670 --> 01:52:15,370
Seo Won chose Min Ju.

2075
01:52:15,370 --> 01:52:18,190
- I say Seo Won.
- She does like him, of course.

2076
01:52:18,190 --> 01:52:20,700
- What do you think?
- Well?

2077
01:52:20,700 --> 01:52:22,480
[Stunned]

2078
01:52:22,480 --> 01:52:25,120
Why are you looking at me like that?

2079
01:52:25,120 --> 01:52:27,290
I think Min Ju will text Seong Min.

2080
01:52:27,290 --> 01:52:29,500
How about Seo Won?

2081
01:52:29,500 --> 01:52:31,830
Is it Gyu Ri or Min Ju?

2082
01:52:31,830 --> 01:52:34,690
- Gyu Ri.
- They were together on the boat.

2083
01:52:34,690 --> 01:52:38,020
They were lovey-dovey together.

2084
01:52:38,020 --> 01:52:39,890
How about a tap-tap-tap picture moment?

2085
01:52:39,890 --> 01:52:42,440
They look good together.

2086
01:52:42,440 --> 01:52:44,600
Gyu Ri. Let's go with Gyu Ri.

2087
01:52:44,600 --> 01:52:47,050
The signal we saw today was Gyu Ri.

2088
01:52:47,050 --> 01:52:49,770
I want to know. How will it turn out?

2089
01:52:49,770 --> 01:52:54,070
[The first night in Tokushima]

2090
01:52:57,650 --> 01:53:00,700
[Desperately waiting for a text from someone]

2091
01:53:01,830 --> 01:53:05,470
Since we're abroad,
it must take longer than usual.

2092
01:53:05,470 --> 01:53:07,350
[Cracking up]

2093
01:53:07,350 --> 01:53:09,790
It must be coming from Korea.

2094
01:53:09,790 --> 01:53:11,750
I feel like my heart will disappear.

2095
01:53:11,750 --> 01:53:14,240
You feel like your heart will disappear?

2096
01:53:14,240 --> 01:53:16,840
Buzz, buzz, buzz.
It will beep about five times.

2097
01:53:16,840 --> 01:53:19,760
- Really?
- I sent you one, too.

2098
01:53:19,760 --> 01:53:22,340
It will buzz five times.

2099
01:53:23,240 --> 01:53:24,310
[Buzz]

2100
01:53:24,310 --> 01:53:28,180
[Yu Gyeong's signal phone buzzes right then]

2101
01:53:28,580 --> 01:53:31,060
I'm thankful I can curl my hair tomorrow.

2102
01:53:31,060 --> 01:53:34,040
[Beluga of the Forest: I hope
we can go on a date tomorrow]

2103
01:53:34,040 --> 01:53:37,000
- That's right.
- Okay.

2104
01:53:39,010 --> 01:53:40,950
Jun Hyeon is making his moves now.

2105
01:53:40,950 --> 01:53:42,870
- Let's go.
- Fighting!

2106
01:53:44,120 --> 01:53:45,130
[Buzz]

2107
01:53:52,110 --> 01:53:54,340
[Busy Hamster: Isn't Japan fun?]

2108
01:53:54,340 --> 01:53:56,350
[Should we not go back?]

2109
01:53:56,350 --> 01:53:58,270
[Let's have fun tomorrow, too]

2110
01:53:58,270 --> 01:54:02,680
[Busy Hamster]

2111
01:54:05,490 --> 01:54:07,150
[Thinking]

2112
01:54:07,150 --> 01:54:08,890
Min Ju...

2113
01:54:09,660 --> 01:54:11,000
[Buzz]

2114
01:54:13,230 --> 01:54:17,000
[Salt Bread: Let's have more fun tomorrow]

2115
01:54:17,000 --> 01:54:21,090
- Okay.
- He's not a bad guy.

2116
01:54:22,050 --> 01:54:24,500
"Let's have more fun tomorrow."

2117
01:54:24,500 --> 01:54:27,480
He's asking her to pick him.

2118
01:54:27,480 --> 01:54:30,210
"Let's have more fun tomorrow."

2119
01:54:30,210 --> 01:54:33,740
- We'll see about Wu Yeol tomorrow.
- That's true.

2120
01:54:36,860 --> 01:54:38,140
[Buzz]

2121
01:54:38,140 --> 01:54:40,710
[Gyu Ri's phone buzzes again]

2122
01:54:41,490 --> 01:54:44,410
[Tired Camel: Have fun tomorrow!]

2123
01:54:45,220 --> 01:54:49,600
[Tired Camel]

2124
01:54:49,600 --> 01:54:52,830
- They pretty much know the nicknames.
- They all know now.

2125
01:54:54,610 --> 01:54:56,780
Seo Won must feel...

2126
01:54:56,780 --> 01:55:00,000
[The night is getting deeper
as they contemplate their choices]

2127
01:55:03,690 --> 01:55:07,030
Now, the texts are letting
their feelings be known.

2128
01:55:07,030 --> 01:55:09,370
This is driving me crazy.

2129
01:55:14,940 --> 01:55:16,020
[Buzz]

2130
01:55:18,270 --> 01:55:20,890
[Pure Rabbit: Rest up and see you
tomorrow in good shape]

2131
01:55:21,670 --> 01:55:26,030
[Pure Rabbit]

2132
01:55:26,030 --> 01:55:30,290
[Failed to guess So Yun's choice]

2133
01:55:31,160 --> 01:55:32,490
Gosh, my head hurts.

2134
01:55:32,490 --> 01:55:37,290
Wow, they're all so straightforward.

2135
01:55:44,690 --> 01:55:46,030
[Buzz]

2136
01:55:51,450 --> 01:55:57,390
[Sleepy Bear: You have a nice smile.
Always smile!]

2137
01:55:58,180 --> 01:56:02,590
[Sleepy Bear]

2138
01:56:02,590 --> 01:56:05,020
[Failed to guess Min Ju's choice, too]

2139
01:56:05,020 --> 01:56:07,230
W-W-Who insisted on this?

2140
01:56:07,230 --> 01:56:10,530
- I said Seong Min.
- She kept saying it's Seong Min.

2141
01:56:10,530 --> 01:56:13,180
Roy, what did you say about Min Ju?

2142
01:56:13,180 --> 01:56:14,250
Me again?

2143
01:56:14,250 --> 01:56:16,700
I don't even remember what I said.

2144
01:56:16,700 --> 01:56:18,220
It was Roy, right?

2145
01:56:18,220 --> 01:56:20,490
We gave it to you.

2146
01:56:20,490 --> 01:56:23,300
We said, let's let him have it.

2147
01:56:23,300 --> 01:56:25,740
What's wrong with Min Ju?

2148
01:56:25,740 --> 01:56:29,090
The love lines have

2149
01:56:29,090 --> 01:56:32,140
- changed a lot compared to before.
- They've changed.

2150
01:56:32,140 --> 01:56:35,060
They just pick the person they like.

2151
01:56:35,060 --> 01:56:37,700
She still chooses him even
after seeing a sorry sight.

2152
01:56:37,700 --> 01:56:41,110
- She picked Seong Min again.
- Isn't she so lovely?

2153
01:56:41,110 --> 01:56:46,790
[Min Ju didn't change
and still texted Seong Min]

2154
01:56:46,790 --> 01:56:49,040
Gosh, seriously.

2155
01:56:50,010 --> 01:56:50,970
[Buzz]

2156
01:56:54,180 --> 01:56:56,200
[My Dog, Yellow: You made me happy today]

2157
01:56:56,200 --> 01:56:57,560
[Let's hang out again]

2158
01:56:57,560 --> 01:57:00,840
- Okay...
- It's Wu Yeol. I told you.

2159
01:57:02,510 --> 01:57:05,000
Roy totally failed.

2160
01:57:05,000 --> 01:57:07,740
[Roy Kim failed to guess once again]

2161
01:57:07,740 --> 01:57:09,690
You're doing this on purpose, right?

2162
01:57:09,690 --> 01:57:11,920
You're after the bidet commercial, right?

2163
01:57:11,920 --> 01:57:13,720
You people are too much.

2164
01:57:13,720 --> 01:57:16,630
You'll get a bidet commercial.
The crappiest intuition ever.

2165
01:57:16,700 --> 01:57:18,500
I'm sorry.

2166
01:57:18,530 --> 01:57:20,020
I'll go to the restroom.

2167
01:57:20,020 --> 01:57:22,110
Yu Gyeong was hard to guess.

2168
01:57:23,080 --> 01:57:24,470
[Buzz]

2169
01:57:25,200 --> 01:57:28,290
[Dried Sweet Potato: I'm glad we got closer]

2170
01:57:28,290 --> 01:57:32,860
- That's right.
- They were so tight.

2171
01:57:32,860 --> 01:57:37,010
Wu Yeol got texts from both
of the ladies of his choice.

2172
01:57:37,010 --> 01:57:38,590
Gosh, this is trouble.

2173
01:57:38,590 --> 01:57:39,960
It's starting over again.

2174
01:57:39,960 --> 01:57:43,940
Gosh, Wu Yeol has got it going on.

2175
01:57:43,940 --> 01:57:45,980
Wu Yeol, should we quit?

2176
01:57:47,120 --> 01:57:51,110
- I want to quit.
- I think it'll be too hard later. I'll quit.

2177
01:57:51,110 --> 01:57:52,920
Tokushima is a tough city.

2178
01:57:52,920 --> 01:57:55,800
Seong Min is hurt because
he didn't get a text from Yu Gyeong.

2179
01:57:55,800 --> 01:58:00,740
It's a conflicting night in Tokushima.

2180
01:58:01,340 --> 01:58:03,390
We've failed more days, right?

2181
01:58:03,400 --> 01:58:05,800
- We almost get them wrong, right?
- On top of that,

2182
01:58:05,800 --> 01:58:08,460
it's all Roy's fault. That's huge.

2183
01:58:08,460 --> 01:58:11,180
I get it now. I understand these people now.

2184
01:58:11,180 --> 01:58:13,880
- You said that last week, too.
- I really get it now.

2185
01:58:13,880 --> 01:58:16,160
I'll get them correct starting next week.

2186
01:58:16,160 --> 01:58:20,180
I think Roy Kim will be the talk
of the town in dating shows.

2187
01:58:20,180 --> 01:58:21,790
This is so annoying.

2188
01:58:21,790 --> 01:58:23,480
You'll continue to sing love songs, right?

2189
01:58:23,480 --> 01:58:25,450
I really don't know what love is.

2190
01:58:25,450 --> 01:58:26,700
Why do people listen to my songs?

2191
01:58:26,700 --> 01:58:29,800
- Your songs will be popular, though.
- "I don't know love."

2192
01:58:29,800 --> 01:58:30,890
- I have no idea.
- Your songs will be popular.

2193
01:58:30,890 --> 01:58:31,940
You'll get dumped.

2194
01:58:31,940 --> 01:58:34,090
How can we wait until next week?

2195
01:58:34,090 --> 01:58:38,560
- Goodnight!
- Let's do one episode per day!

2196
01:58:38,560 --> 01:58:40,650
[The wind blows]

2197
01:58:40,650 --> 01:58:42,730
Who's your top choice?

2198
01:58:42,730 --> 01:58:44,940
For me...

2199
01:58:44,940 --> 01:58:48,140
I told you. Love is all about timing.

2200
01:58:49,930 --> 01:58:53,470
I think the person I expected will be there.

2201
01:58:53,470 --> 01:58:55,960
I decided to put in the effort.

2202
01:58:55,960 --> 01:58:58,240
[I'll show you how I've changed]

2203
01:58:59,820 --> 01:59:05,860
I tend to decide pretty quickly.

2204
01:59:05,860 --> 01:59:09,730
When I'm with you, I feel so calm.

2205
01:59:10,990 --> 01:59:14,800
I want to speak casually with you.

2206
01:59:16,080 --> 01:59:19,200
[Riding this wind...]

2207
01:59:19,200 --> 01:59:21,960
I think there are about two people.

2208
01:59:21,960 --> 01:59:24,770
Am I one of those two?

2209
01:59:24,770 --> 01:59:29,080
I did think I would change
my mind after the trip.

2210
01:59:29,950 --> 01:59:33,600
I didn't think it was helpful to speak up.

2211
01:59:34,650 --> 01:59:39,300
My eyes were drawn to you the most.

2212
01:59:39,300 --> 01:59:41,400
I think something changed from that point on.

2213
01:59:41,400 --> 01:59:44,480
He's a man with such a different vibe.

2214
01:59:44,480 --> 01:59:47,560
What's this?
You two are wearing the same rings.

2215
01:59:47,560 --> 01:59:49,960
You're wearing rings?

2216
01:59:51,380 --> 01:59:53,710
It's tough.

2217
01:59:53,710 --> 01:59:55,070
As much as my heart trembled?

2218
01:59:55,070 --> 01:59:57,260
I don't think I'm afraid.

2219
01:59:57,260 --> 01:59:59,240
Are you ready?
